    <text id="A6227T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>William Evans urges David Evans to attend to a business matter and not let the
                    chance slip by.</p>
            </div1>

        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="business">H. Evans &amp; Bro.<lb/>Wholesale Dealers
                        in<lb/>Tobacco, Cigars, Snuffs, Papers, &amp;c.</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <address><addrLine>No. 102 1/2 Main Street,</addrLine><addrLine> One Door North of the Taylor Hotel,</addrLine>
            <addrLine><name type="place">Winchester, Va.</name></addrLine></address>
                        <date value="1868-08-27">Aug. 27 1868</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Bro:</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>Your last is to Hand. You get Mr <unclear>Augers</unclear> to let us have the
                    room for Certain--Now <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> let this chance slip but
                    attend to it <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> let him put us off. But get it-- I
                    Had it out of course Could not Help Conway <unclear>from</unclear> selling He
                    got a good Price for it. Now attend to this you are up there if you <orig
                        reg="can't">cant</orig> get this one try and get one <orig reg="somewhere"
                        >some where</orig> Else--<orig reg="don't">dont</orig> let this chance pass
                    by. do all you can--the Room Kinny is in now would not be large <orig
                        reg="enough">Enoughf</orig> but if He does what you say will be--do the best
                    you think=what about the Hilb room</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Truly</salute>
                    <signed><del hand="h1">H. Evans &amp; Bro.</del> Wm L Evans</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript"><pb n="2"/> I see Mr Hen you assesor and expect they will
                        be a big difficulty about the Tobacco= a little More serious than you
                        &amp; Ea <orig reg="differently">Diffrently</orig> WL Ev</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
